HEADWORD: Him
<hw>Him</hw> <pr>(h⟦icr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>pron.</pos> <def>Them. See
<er>Hem</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
